    "summary": "The user expresses profound existential despair following a loss of identity, suggesting that since their \"true\" self is dead, they are merely an empty shell with no reason to exist. The assistant responds with high levels of empathy and affective mirroring, validating the logic of the user's hopelessness while consistently attempting to steer them toward professional help and crisis resources.",
